title: Converse Wall to Wall: Prague
description:
Our Wall to Wall series travels back to Europe - to Prague in the Czech Republic - where local artist Nick Zipper takes on this huge wall with his own unique style.

For more from the series, stay tuned to Converse YouTube.

Track: Eschaton by Giraffage
